Let's assume you have this code:

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace Data;

use RuntimeException as MyLocallyRenamedException;

class Exception extends MyLocallyRe
{
}
```

When you hit `Ctrl`+`Space` at the end of the `class Exception extends MyLocallyRe` line, PDT completes the line with this UI;

![immagine](https://github.com/eclipse/pdt/assets/928116/e01be630-aa71-4d0a-bcaf-f8bf184bfb24)

Shouldn't PDT list only `MyLocallyRenamedException` as defined in the same file? It instead shows all the `RuntimeException` classes in the project.

