```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace Data;

use RuntimeException as MyLocallyRenamedException;

class Exception extends \MyLocallyRenamedException
{
}
```

Which is rather wrong: there's no `MyLocallyRenamedException` class defined in the root namespace.


